---
---

<section class="jungle-section" id="jungle">
  <!-- Left: photo with parallax -->
  <div class="jungle-img-col">
    <div class="parallax-img-wrap" id="jungle-img-wrap">
      <img src="/images/jungle.webp" alt="Jungle waterfall, Southeast Asia" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right: dark green text panel -->
  <div class="jungle-text-col">
    <div class="section-eyebrow" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)">
      <span class="eyebrow-num">005</span>
      <span class="eyebrow-line" style="background:var(--moss)"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow-text">Southeast Asia</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title" aria-label="Jungle Falls">
      <span class="line">JUNGLE</span>
      <span class="line moss-accent">FALLS</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="section-body" style="color:var(--mist, #8FA88A)">
      The forest floor was permanent dusk.
      Mist drifted in from the cascade and settled
      on every leaf. <em>Nothing moved quickly here</em> —
      the jungle runs on its own logic,
      its own deep time.
    </p>

    <blockquote class="jungle-quote">
      "The waterfall had no beginning we could find —
      it simply arrived, white and absolute,
      from somewhere above the canopy."
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

